{
  "texts": [
    "Therefore, the methods employed herein should be adapted and applied across different educational levels to assess the consistency of results, given the varying nature of writing styles encountered.",
    "For instance, tools deployed at the university level should undergo fine-tuning to discern AI-generated writing specific to that academic setting, ensuring precision and relevance in detection.",
    "Moreover, it's crucial to employ these methods with diverse datasets comprising students from varied backgrounds and academic years, following a panel data structure.",
    "This approach enables the assessment of accuracy while also facilitating the identification of potential biases.",
    "This research explores the impact of the Transformer methodology, particularly in the realm of Natural Language Processing (NLP)."
  ]
}